<DOCNO> NYT19980619.0094 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-19 12:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7041 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JAPAN-US-HNS &LR;      06-19 0580
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JAPAN-US-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
JAPAN'S ASSURANCES MEET WITH SKEPTICISM 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (EDs: FILED in ``i'' and ``f'' categories)   News Analysis  
