<P>
   MUSIC-MCLACHLAN (Undated) _ Sarah McLachlan hopes to raise lots
more money for charity on this year's Lilith Fair tour.
</P>
<P>
   By Gene Stout. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   WORKPLACE-COLUMN-SMITH (Undated) _ Bosses have long suspected
their workers are getting less loyal. Now there is evidence.
</P>
<P>
   By Carol Smith. (Story will move in the ``f'' category.)
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-06-19-98 1414EDT &QL; 
