travel agent request a room on a high floor ending in the numbers
36, 37, 38, 39, 41, 43 or 44, which all face the western hills.
</P>
<P>
   From these rooms, you will directly overlook the red and yellow
pitched roofs of the Forbidden City, and with binoculars can see
details of the morning flag-raising on Tiananmen Square. The scene
is unmatched.
</P>
<P>
   (Cox Newspapers Asia correspondents Marcia Kunstel and Joseph
Albright are based in Beijing.)
