   ELDER _ Elder-Beerman Stores Corp. has agreed to buy Stone &AMP;
Thomas, a small department store chain based in Wheeling, W. Va.,
for $38 million. Stone &AMP; Thomas operates 21 stores in West
Virginia, Ohio and Kentucky. (Bohman, Dayton Daily News) ETA 8 p.m.
ET.
</P>
<P>
   DUNLAP-BEHAVIOR _ Al Dunlap's job wasn't on the line when
Sunbeam Corp's. board of directors gathered in New York early last
week. Rather, the seven directors, including Dunlap, met June 9 to
discuss how to answer a national magazine's allegations against the
company. But Dunlap's behavior at the meeting set in motion a
series of events that led to his firing just four days later.
(Waresh, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
