<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-19 19:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7922 &Cx1f; tth-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BUDGET-SPOT-SPI &LR;      06-19 0091
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BUDGET-SPOT-SPI </SLUG>
  
