addressed the largest national gathering of Latino politicians. One
major issue to be discussed at the conference is affirmative
action. By LORI RODRIGUEZ.
</P>
<P>
   HOMELESS-HEAT (Houston) _ Homeless shelters do their largest
business in the winter, but these dog days have prompted at least
one shelter, the Salvation Army Harbor Light Center in Houston, to
offer refuge from the heat during the daytime hours. By CARLOS
BYARS.
</P>
