<P>
   BBA-REDSOX-RAYS (St. Petersburg, Fla.) _ By Gordon Edes.
</P>
<P>
   YAC-BERMUDA (Newport, R.I.) _ In picture-perfect weather, the
largest fleet of boats in 16 years took off for Bermuda in the
biennial showcase of blue-water racing on the East Coast. By Tony
Chamberlain.
</P>
<P>
   MCDONOUGH-COLUMN (Undated) _ The Chicago Bulls learned how to
win championships from Detroit. By Will McDonough.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
