<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GM20-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    No green light: Talks between GM and UAW at a stand still
 &HT;    By Mike Wagner
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
