<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-19 20:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8160 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MINOR-RIGHTS-$ADV21-H     06-19 1720
