<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Monday, June 15,
about the confusing language of physics at international
conferences misattributed a comment about professors' making better
speakers than graduate students. It was from Dr. Sheldon Glashow of
Harvard, not Dr. Maurice Goldhaber, former director of the
Brookhaven National Laboratory in Long Island.
