<HEADLINE>
ABANDONED TEXAS COMMUNITY BEGUN BY FORMER SLAVES WILL AGAIN COME TO
LIFE
</HEADLINE>
 (Resending to fix summary line) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MARY SALTARELLI 
c.1997 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   GRANBURY, Texas _ A Hood County community settled more than a
